Scanners

Class CTableDrivenScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • Scanners.CScanner
      • Scanners.CTableDrivenScanner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IScanner
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDFAScanner

    public abstract class CTableDrivenScanner
extends CScanner
    CScanner_DFABase is an abstract base class which descends from CScanner and intended to be a base class for both DFA-driven scanners (i.e. scanners using a CDFA object) and generated DFA scanners (i.e. scanners where the tables have been generated as constant definitions in a Java compilation unit).
